# =====================================================
# CORS CONFIGURATION
# =====================================================

# WHAT:
# - Kaunse frontend domain ko backend access allowed hai

# WHY:
# - Frontend aur backend different ports/domains pe hote hain
# - Browser security ke liye CORS required hota hai

